00:05:19.402 --> 00:05:21.571 align:middle line:84%
And the second is
called the monitor.

00:05:21.571 --> 00:05:23.448 align:middle line:84%
And the role of the
monitor is simple.

00:05:23.448 --> 00:05:26.618 align:middle line:84%
The role of the monitor
