into a deeper sleep.

00:05:40.549 --> 00:05:42.801 align:middle line:84%
The monitor guides
the viewer, step

00:05:42.801 --> 00:05:47.389 align:middle line:84%
by step, to help them focus on
things like a precise location

00:05:47.389 --> 00:05:51.058 align:middle line:84%
